Task Explanation-
The task is to create a simple web page using HTML and CSS that displays an image along with a caption.

A heading is added to describe the content (My Favorite Place)
An image is displayed using the <img> tag (from an online source)
A short paragraph is written below the image as a caption
Basic CSS is used to:
Center the content
Style the text
Adjust the image size

Objective-
To understand how to:

Structure a basic HTML page
Display images on a webpage
Apply simple CSS styling
